Reasoning: The paper involves natural language processing (NLP) techniques to extract information from clinical reports, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also involves computer vision techniques to analyze chest X-rays, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The use of deep learning models for prediction falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves information retrieval techniques to construct a training set, which falls under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper involves multimedia analysis of medical images, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM).
